                        <interp inst="t18401214-name-424" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18401214-name-424" type="surname" value="HAGAR"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18401214-name-424" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>CHARLES HAGAR</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a policeman. The prosecutor called me, and I took the prisoners—this property was found under their waistcoats, next their bodies—each of them had a portion—Cotter had on one stocking which belongs to the lodger—the things were quite wet.</p>
